questiondata.strat-other: I was visualizing words that came one after the other together. Like a someone in a "mummy" "costume" in a "barrel" with a "sparrow" on their head in the back of a pickup truck with a "cook" being the "driver", a "viking" on a "dragon", a "shark" being a "farmer", an "actress" in a "motel" room with a "dresser", "antler"s on the wall, looking at a "sunrise" out the window when suddenly she becomes the "victim" of a murder, etc.
